<i>Get your revenge!</i>

1918
02:16:47,243 --> 02:16:53,560
<i>300 years asleep, haunted
by painful thoughts</i>

1919
02:16:52,413 --> 02:16:54,546
{\an8}<i>(Wry wry, we vow to kill!)</i>

1920
02:16:54,757 --> 02:16:57,010
{\an8}<i>(Wry wry, we vow to destroy!)</i>

1921
02:16:57,180 --> 02:16:59,272
{\an8}<i>(Wry wry!)</i>

1922
02:17:00,060 --> 02:17:01,638
Wait, Dio!

1923
02:17:01,782 --> 02:17:03,996
{\an8}<i>(Wry wry!)</i>

1924
02:17:04,119 --> 02:17:06,360
Come quick, JoJo.

1925
02:17:06,487 --> 02:17:08,622
{\an8}<i>(Wry wry!)</i>

1926
02:17:08,753 --> 02:17:12,744
My world is in the palm of my hand now!

1927
02:17:11,171 --> 02:17:13,012
{\an8}<i>(Wry wry!)</i>

1928
02:17:15,748 --> 02:17:18,072
<i>(Wry wry, we vow to kill!)</i>

1929
02:17:18,099 --> 02:17:20,442
<i>(Wry wry, we vow to destroy!)</i>

1930
02:17:20,701 --> 02:17:24,309
<i>I will dominate life at last,</i>

1931
02:17:24,820 --> 02:17:29,970
<i>Tearing its natural
order from God’s grasp</i>

1932
02:17:30,336 --> 02:17:33,693
<i>I will dominate history too,</i>

1933
02:17:33,857 --> 02:17:39,352
<i>Rewriting and upending it anew</i>

1934
02:17:39,722 --> 02:17:42,889
<i>I will dominate even time,</i>

1935
02:17:42,930 --> 02:17:46,809
<i>My body eternal and sublime</i>

1936
02:17:45,787 --> 02:17:48,652
{\an8}<i>(Eternal life!)</i>

1937
02:17:49,067 --> 02:17:56,901
<i>I will dominate everything,
rise above all my cares</i>

1938
02:17:55,205 --> 02:17:58,007
{\an8}<i>(We vow to steal them away!)</i>

1939
02:17:58,178 --> 02:18:02,639
<i>Win it all, negate righteousness</i>

1940
02:18:02,687 --> 02:18:06,500
<i>In this peacefully unaware country</i>

1941
02:18:04,347 --> 02:18:07,539
{\an8}<i>(This country is ours!)</i>

1942
02:18:07,742 --> 02:18:13,511
<i>I will dominate everything,
I’ll face them now</i>

1943
02:18:13,576 --> 02:18:16,899
<i>And demand peace of mind!</i>

1944
02:18:16,443 --> 02:18:18,559
{\an8}<i>(Wry wry, we vow to kill!)</i>

1945
02:18:17,679 --> 02:18:22,854
<i>My world, this world!</i>

1946
02:18:18,817 --> 02:18:20,955
{\an8}<i>(Wry wry, we vow to destroy!)</i>

1947
02:18:23,428 --> 02:18:24,571
<i>Wry wry!</i>

1948
02:18:24,606 --> 02:18:29,446
<i>This is Dio’s World!</i>

1949
02:18:37,941 --> 02:18:40,261
It’s melting...

1950
02:18:40,549 --> 02:18:42,726
It’s really melting away...

1951
02:18:42,752 --> 02:18:44,988
So much that there’s a hole in my cheek...

1952
02:18:45,237 --> 02:18:47,116
My tongue is sticking out of the hole!

1953
02:18:47,500 --> 02:18:49,165
Your cheek is melting,

1954
02:18:50,973 --> 02:18:53,607
And your tongue is sticking
out of the hole? Really, Jack?

1955
02:18:53,627 --> 02:18:54,341
Dio!

1956
02:18:54,351 --> 02:18:55,351
Oh, it really is.

1957
02:18:59,005 --> 02:19:01,055
The sun has set.

1958
02:19:02,448 --> 02:19:06,948
It’s time for your lives
to go down with it!

1959
02:19:07,311 --> 02:19:10,400
I’ve been building up my
courage for this moment!

1960
02:19:10,533 --> 02:19:12,603
Even so, I can’t help
this feeling of dread.

1961
02:19:12,627 --> 02:19:14,698
As a human, I can’t let
you get away with this!

1962
02:19:14,725 --> 02:19:15,725
JoJo!

1963
02:19:16,793 --> 02:19:18,499
Put your training to use.

1964
02:19:30,221 --> 02:19:33,425
<i>(We’ll feast! On your blood and flesh!)</i>

1965
02:19:34,306 --> 02:19:36,070
<i>(Steal it away!)</i>

1966
02:19:37,052 --> 02:19:39,713
<i>(To heal all of our wounds!)</i>

1967
02:19:39,771 --> 02:19:42,735
<i>JoJo, here’s a lesson for you</i>

1968
02:19:44,050 --> 02:19:49,405
<i>The north wind made the vikings!</i>

1969
02:19:49,525 --> 02:19:50,930
This battle will be an exercise—

1970
02:19:50,955 --> 02:19:53,981
You’ll defeat them without spilling
a single drop of wine from this glass!

1971
02:19:54,038 --> 02:19:56,957
SPW: We’re not here to play around, have you lost it?
ZEP: You shut your trap!

1972
02:19:57,017 --> 02:19:58,982
The north wind made the vikings!

1973
02:19:59,918 --> 02:20:02,859
JACK: I’ll kill them!
DIO: Ah—wait, wait—

1974
02:20:08,274 --> 02:20:12,710
<i>Tough vikings were born
from the harsh north wind</i>

1975
02:20:13,014 --> 02:20:16,820
<i>Will this wine make a viking out of you?</i>

1976
02:20:16,468 --> 02:20:17,609
{\an8}<i>(Give us your blood!)</i>

1977
02:20:17,706 --> 02:20:22,238
<i>Make fear your own!
Here’s a battle lesson:</i>

1978
02:20:22,315 --> 02:20:26,689
<i>Muster up your courage! When the time
comes, don’t let your breathing go awry!</i>

1979
02:20:26,947 --> 02:20:30,788
<i>The hymn of humanity is a song of courage!</i>

1980
02:20:31,192 --> 02:20:35,529
<i>The greatness of humanity is
the greatness of courage!</i>

1981
02:20:35,769 --> 02:20:41,540
<i>Everything is connected!
There’s a meaning to it all!</i>

1982
02:20:42,057 --> 02:20:44,369
<i>Don’t let your breathing go awry!</i>

1983
02:20:48,222 --> 02:20:49,278
{\an8}<i>(Wry!)</i>

1984
02:20:48,445 --> 02:20:50,720
<i>This wine will be my north wind!</i>

1985
02:20:49,749 --> 02:20:51,164
{\an8}<i>(Give us your blood!)</i>

1986
02:20:50,783 --> 02:20:52,800
<i>The ripple of the wine!</i>

1987
02:20:52,130 --> 02:20:53,942
{\an8}<i>(We’ll feast on your flesh!)</i>

1988
02:20:53,459 --> 02:20:57,661
<i>I can feel it flow, I’ll find my
way through the darkness!</i>

1989
02:20:57,788 --> 02:21:00,128
<i>The waves of the ripple!</i>

1990
02:20:59,237 --> 02:21:00,565
{\an8}<i>(Give us your blood!)</i>

1991
02:21:00,264 --> 02:21:02,416
<i>Are resounding through my body!</i>

1992
02:21:01,528 --> 02:21:02,766
{\an8}<i>(We’ll feast on your flesh!)</i>

1993
02:21:02,568 --> 02:21:04,560
<i>With the power of the sun!</i>

1994
02:21:04,588 --> 02:21:07,371
<i>Find your way through the darkness!</i>

1995
02:21:07,439 --> 02:21:10,893
<i>Oh, my heart resonates!</i>

1996
02:21:11,402 --> 02:21:17,314
<i>Pa-pow-pow-pow with unrelenting heat!</i>

1997
02:21:15,472 --> 02:21:16,472
{\an8}<i>(Heat!)</i>

1998
02:21:17,421 --> 02:21:18,516
<i>Sunlight...</i>

1999
02:21:18,554 --> 02:21:19,687
<i>(Sunlight...)</i>

2000
02:21:19,700 --> 02:21:20,889
<i>Yellow...</i>

2001
02:21:20,927 --> 02:21:22,115
<i>(Yellow...)</i>

2002
02:21:22,130 --> 02:21:23,151
<i>Over...</i>

2003
02:21:23,185 --> 02:21:23,824
<i>(Over!)</i>

2004
02:21:23,862 --> 02:21:25,495
<i>Sunlight yellow, sunlight yellow</i>

2005
02:21:25,556 --> 02:21:34,259
<i>Overdrive!!</i>

2006
02:21:40,767 --> 02:21:43,241
The ripple of the sun! Dio!

2007
02:21:43,270 --> 02:21:45,778
This is the power
that will defeat you!

2008
02:21:49,430 --> 02:21:51,019
Dio Brando?

2009
02:21:51,067 --> 02:21:52,067
Yeah?

2010
02:21:52,476 --> 02:21:54,745
I don’t know you, but...

2011
02:21:55,840 --> 02:22:00,911
Let me say this to the Stone
Mask that awakened your brain:

2012
02:22:02,219 --> 02:22:04,236
Finally, we meet.

2013
02:22:04,583 --> 02:22:06,499
Don’t get carried away!

2014
02:22:11,812 --> 02:22:16,956
Perhaps you can heal this
wound in my stomach, JoJo.

2015
02:22:19,693 --> 02:22:22,325
You’re the one who put it there!

2016
02:22:23,028 --> 02:22:27,647
Then I’ll be completely healed from
the damage you dealt me in that fire.

2017
02:22:29,278 --> 02:22:31,738
I’ll be using your lives...

2018
02:22:32,221 --> 02:22:35,513
To purge this wound!

2019
02:22:35,540 --> 02:22:36,825
You bastard!

2020
02:22:36,857 --> 02:22:40,831
Just how many lives did you
extinguish to heal that wound?

2021
02:22:47,555 --> 02:22:56,219
Do you remember how many slices of
bread you’ve eaten in your lifetime?

2022
02:23:02,207 --> 02:23:04,723
I’ll make you submit!

2023
02:23:06,393 --> 02:23:08,172
By the ripple of the sun!

2024
02:23:09,357 --> 02:23:10,567
Pow!

2025
02:23:10,965 --> 02:23:14,251
Utterly pathetic!

2026
02:23:14,298 --> 02:23:16,075
It’s freezing?!

2027
02:23:16,207 --> 02:23:20,902
I guessed that this energy of yours
is related to the flow of your blood!

2028
02:23:20,956 --> 02:23:25,641
I am able to control my own body at will.

2029
02:23:26,795 --> 02:23:29,529
If I freeze up all of your veins,

2030
02:23:29,880 --> 02:23:32,767
Then you won’t be able to use that power!

2031
02:23:33,504 --> 02:23:35,647
I can’t—I can’t catch my breath!

2032
02:23:36,284 --> 02:23:37,503
Mr. Zeppeli!

2033
02:23:39,969 --> 02:23:42,758
Useless, useless, useless, useless!

2034
02:23:44,532 --> 02:23:48,087
Breathing techniques? Ripple?

2035
02:23:49,380 --> 02:23:52,056
If you’re going to be
blowing all this hot air,

2036
02:23:52,101 --> 02:23:57,326
You ought to use it to
play me a little fanfare!

2037
02:24:04,018 --> 02:24:08,359
Looks like your companions
are just as weak as you.

2038
02:24:08,396 --> 02:24:10,305
JOJO: What did you say?
DIO: Companions...

2039
02:24:11,687 --> 02:24:15,053
That’s right. Do you remember?

2040
02:24:15,487 --> 02:24:19,836
The story of the knights
your father told us that day?

2041
02:24:19,892 --> 02:24:20,895
What?

2042
02:24:20,969 --> 02:24:26,152
The tragic queen who was sentenced
to beheading by Elizabeth the First,

2043
02:24:26,315 --> 02:24:30,243
After a failed assassination
plot in the 1600s...

2044
02:24:30,770 --> 02:24:32,921
Mary Stuart!

2045
02:24:34,146 --> 02:24:35,986
It was about the ones who served her!

2046
02:24:36,699 --> 02:24:41,248
The story of those two proud knights...

2047
02:24:41,858 --> 02:24:42,835
Father told us...

2048
02:24:42,870 --> 02:24:43,870
Yes!

2049
02:24:44,214 --> 02:24:47,898
We listened to it together, didn’t we?!

2050
02:24:49,345 --> 02:24:51,557
JoJo, Dio!

2051
02:24:51,644 --> 02:24:54,313
I will regale you with
a tale of two knights,

2052
02:24:54,370 --> 02:24:57,016
Which has been passed down for
generations in our great England.

2053
02:24:57,818 --> 02:25:00,986
Those who lived with a gentleman’s spirit—

2054
02:25:01,023 --> 02:25:04,104
This is a story of knightly pride!

2055
02:25:06,083 --> 02:25:10,502
<i>Long ago, 300 years before today</i>

2056
02:25:10,732 --> 02:25:15,077
<i>Two queens battled for the throne</i>

2057
02:25:15,281 --> 02:25:19,667
<i>One was Queen Elizabeth the First</i>

2058
02:25:19,836 --> 02:25:23,953
<i>And the other, the beautiful Mary Stuart</i>

2059
02:25:24,341 --> 02:25:28,443
<i>Two legendary heroes came forward,</i>

2060
02:25:28,928 --> 02:25:32,412
<i>Offering up their swords to serve Mary</i>

2061
02:25:33,562 --> 02:25:41,659
<i>Tarkus’s strength cleaved
through rocks like butter</i>

2062
02:25:41,860 --> 02:25:50,852
<i>Bruford, with his skill and spirit,
cut down foes like a phantom</i>

2063
02:25:51,714 --> 02:25:56,262
<i>Without any family, the
two honed their powers</i>

2064
02:25:56,313 --> 02:26:00,432
<i>While wishing for a nest to rest in</i>

2065
02:26:00,778 --> 02:26:05,295
<i>After finding peace in Mary’s affections,</i>

2066
02:26:05,346 --> 02:26:09,596
<i>They swore their loyalty to her</i>

2067
02:26:10,093 --> 02:26:14,012
But one day, Elizabeth
accused their master, Mary,

2068
02:26:14,060 --> 02:26:18,222
Of murdering her husband,
and she was captured.

2069
02:26:19,243 --> 02:26:23,236
<i>The two heroes would not rest</i>

2070
02:26:23,545 --> 02:26:27,690
<i>When it came to saving their Mary</i>

2071
02:26:28,093 --> 02:26:32,523
<i>In order to stop those two heroes,</i>

2072
02:26:32,600 --> 02:26:37,007
<i>Elizabeth made an appeal:</i>

2073
02:26:37,105 --> 02:26:41,440
<i>“You two, surrender at once!”</i>

2074
02:26:41,659 --> 02:26:46,159
<i>“And I will spare your master’s life!”</i>

2075
02:26:46,234 --> 02:26:54,555
<i>This, we cannot refuse</i>

2076
02:26:54,672 --> 02:26:59,451
<i>In this, we hold no regrets</i>

2077
02:26:59,534 --> 02:27:04,713
<i>For our queen is our life!</i>

2078
02:27:05,102 --> 02:27:07,235
But in the moment they
were to be executed—

2079
02:27:07,286 --> 02:27:09,698
I’ll give you a little souvenir
before your trip to Hell!

2080
02:27:09,726 --> 02:27:12,216
Your master isn’t being held in the tower.

2081
02:27:12,301 --> 02:27:14,572
I cut off her head myself just yesterday!

2082
02:27:14,651 --> 02:27:17,930
Look at her lying over
there like a piece of rubbish!

2083
02:27:18,017 --> 02:27:22,563
After all, if she was left alive,
we’d risk a rebellion!

2084
02:27:27,263 --> 02:27:30,958
<i>You’ve betrayed us, Elizabeth</i>

2085
02:27:31,033 --> 02:27:35,909
<i>We curse you with our grudge!</i>

2086
02:27:36,414 --> 02:27:40,849
<i>We curse you for all eternity!</i>

2087
02:27:40,940 --> 02:27:45,400
<i>Stiff with rage, Tarkus’s
muscles were like iron</i>

2088
02:27:45,486 --> 02:27:49,590
<i>They couldn’t cut through his neck!</i>

2089
02:27:49,667 --> 02:27:54,502
<i>Bruford, filled with regret,
ensnared them with his hair</i>

2090
02:27:54,590 --> 02:27:57,949
<i>As though it were alive!</i>

2091
02:27:58,005 --> 02:28:00,068
<i>And that is the story,</i>

2092
02:28:00,123 --> 02:28:07,519
<i>Of those knights who lived
according to their hearts</i>

2093
02:28:09,933 --> 02:28:17,235
<i>Until the very end!</i>

2094
02:28:17,608 --> 02:28:19,301
Such blind devotion—
it gives me goosebumps!

2095
02:28:19,345 --> 02:28:20,955
Oh, what loyal hearts!

2096
02:28:21,003 --> 02:28:23,550
But those two should
have done a better job!

2097
02:28:23,604 --> 02:28:26,040
In the end, they couldn’t do
anything from down in the mud.

2098
02:28:26,067 --> 02:28:28,178
The only thing to call
their deaths is useless!

2099
02:28:28,229 --> 02:28:30,589
It might be as you say, however—

2100
02:28:30,639 --> 02:28:32,673
There is nothing that is without meaning.

2101
02:28:32,728 --> 02:28:35,832
The same can be said about the
fact that you came here to this house.

2102
02:28:36,091 --> 02:28:37,541
Everything is connected!

2103
02:28:37,571 --> 02:28:41,304
I want to believe that they
kept on looking at the stars!

2104
02:28:42,991 --> 02:28:47,469
<i>All people live in a prison called fate</i>

2105
02:28:47,546 --> 02:28:51,947
<i>Reaching out through those bars,</i>

2106
02:28:52,025 --> 02:28:56,683
<i>Do they see the stars? Or the mud?</i>

2107
02:28:56,781 --> 02:29:03,657
<i>Either one—</i>

2108
02:29:04,538 --> 02:29:05,638
<i>JoJo</i>

2109
02:29:06,686 --> 02:29:07,786
<i>Dio</i>

2110
02:29:08,654 --> 02:29:15,042
<i>Could be said to be correct!</i>

2111
02:29:23,513 --> 02:29:25,599
I turned those two

2112
02:29:25,876 --> 02:29:31,317
Into vengeful revenants that
would send even the devil running!

2113
02:29:32,237 --> 02:29:37,793
Even history bends before me!

2114
02:29:37,832 --> 02:29:39,032
It can’t be!

2115
02:29:47,594 --> 02:29:49,792
Such grotesque forms!

2116
02:29:49,832 --> 02:29:54,410
It’s the perfect form for
taking their revenge!

2117
02:29:55,069 --> 02:29:57,293
Don’t you think so?

2118
02:29:58,351 --> 02:30:00,971
Kill them all!

2119
02:30:01,232 --> 02:30:03,470
Continue from where
you left off on that day!

2120
02:30:03,522 --> 02:30:04,607
Tarkus!

2121
02:30:04,619 --> 02:30:05,642
Bruford!

2122
02:30:06,182 --> 02:30:09,471
Play me a fanfare with their screams!

2123
02:30:09,864 --> 02:30:12,523
Our grudge!

2124
02:30:12,552 --> 02:30:14,829
Our pride!

2125
02:30:14,854 --> 02:30:16,736
Great Dark Knight Bruford!

2126
02:30:17,083 --> 02:30:18,193
And you, Tarkus!

2127
02:30:18,959 --> 02:30:20,418
The way you feel—

2128
02:30:20,911 --> 02:30:23,111
Your pride, your resentment.

2129
02:30:25,269 --> 02:30:27,042
I can’t even imagine it!

2130
02:30:28,023 --> 02:30:31,214
But I also bear my own burdens!

2131
02:30:31,303 --> 02:30:34,383
I’m gonna be the one to eat ‘em!

2132
02:30:34,676 --> 02:30:37,926
I’ll savour every bit of his cartilage!

2133
02:30:41,531 --> 02:30:43,809
That man’s pride...

2134
02:30:43,836 --> 02:30:45,967
I will stand to meet it, as a knight!

2135
02:30:46,253 --> 02:30:48,867
My master—I, Bruford,

2136
02:30:49,104 --> 02:30:53,346
Would like to be the one to bring
an end to this brave man’s life!

2137
02:30:53,383 --> 02:30:55,518
Alright, go ahead!

2138
02:30:57,907 --> 02:30:59,463
We’ll duel as knights!

2139
02:31:03,166 --> 02:31:04,092
Run away, you two!

2140
02:31:04,102 --> 02:31:04,739
Mr. Joestar!

2141
02:31:04,772 --> 02:31:05,772
Tarkus!

2142
02:31:07,836 --> 02:31:11,106
I won’t let you interfere!

2143
02:31:25,134 --> 02:31:32,549
<i>A wedge driven into the
wasteland of my memory</i>

2144
02:31:32,905 --> 02:31:40,375
<i>At dawn, a blood-red sun
rose over the Atlantic Ocean</i>

2145
02:31:42,821 --> 02:31:43,708
Old man!

2146
02:31:43,724 --> 02:31:45,382
Don’t come any closer!

2147
02:31:51,539 --> 02:31:52,539
Damn it...

2148
02:31:54,239 --> 02:31:55,839
Fucking hell!

2149
02:31:57,328 --> 02:32:01,423
<i>There’s nothing I can do,
I’m a mere spectator</i>

2150
02:32:01,500 --> 02:32:05,207
<i>I’ve got nothing, I’m powerless</i>

2151
02:32:05,476 --> 02:32:09,214
<i>Come on, get real,
even at a time like this?</i>

2152
02:32:09,260 --> 02:32:13,454
<i>Even if I give up, the pain
will just be for another day</i>

2153
02:32:13,581 --> 02:32:16,488
<i>And tomorrow, yes tomorrow,</i>

2154
02:32:16,854 --> 02:32:21,944
<i>I’ll still be over here crying like a loser</i>

2155
02:32:24,090 --> 02:32:25,241
Honourable knight,

2156
02:32:25,814 --> 02:32:27,836
Is revenge your answer?

2157
02:32:28,309 --> 02:32:30,299
Is that what you take pride in?

2158
02:32:31,735 --> 02:32:35,296
If you want to preach, then fight
with your pride on the line!

2159
02:32:35,482 --> 02:32:37,549
You can lecture me after you win!

2160
02:32:37,603 --> 02:32:40,722
<i>Now’s the time, to let
courage resonate in my heart</i>

2161
02:32:40,765 --> 02:32:45,114
<i>I’m not scared of pain</i>

2162
02:32:45,177 --> 02:32:48,915
<i>I must find the strength to stand up</i>

2163
02:32:48,954 --> 02:32:51,883
<i>Tomorrow, tomorrow, tomorrow,</i>

2164
02:32:51,978 --> 02:32:54,205
<i>Tomorrow is right now!</i>

2165
02:32:54,305 --> 02:32:55,638
Old man!

2166
02:33:01,445 --> 02:33:03,814
Melt!

2167
02:33:04,116 --> 02:33:07,345
I didn’t follow you to
become a hindrance!

2168
02:33:07,597 --> 02:33:08,797
Speedwagon...

2169
02:33:09,865 --> 02:33:13,405
<i>I’ll let courage resonate in my heart</i>

2170
02:33:13,465 --> 02:33:17,450
<i>And look the enemy in the eyes</i>

2171
02:33:17,996 --> 02:33:21,464
<i>Won’t wait for a distant tomorrow</i>

2172
02:33:21,508 --> 02:33:25,377
<i>I’ll start walking,</i>

2173
02:33:25,444 --> 02:33:33,134
<i>Find the strength to
get back on my feet</i>

2174
02:33:33,706 --> 02:33:40,245
<i>Tomorrow is now!</i>

2175
02:33:40,402 --> 02:33:41,402
JoJo!

2176
02:33:44,972 --> 02:33:48,028
Cut finely, beat of my blood!

2177
02:33:55,635 --> 02:33:59,095
Please... This knight’s proud heart,

2178
02:33:59,128 --> 02:34:01,192
Let it somehow be restored!

2179
02:34:01,785 --> 02:34:05,509
I am the Dark Knight Bruford!

2180
02:34:06,341 --> 02:34:09,728
This pain means nothing to me!

2181
02:34:16,200 --> 02:34:17,849
Why aren’t you moving?

2182
02:34:21,208 --> 02:34:22,408
Just now,

2183
02:34:25,118 --> 02:34:26,638
You said “pain”.

2184
02:34:29,469 --> 02:34:30,719
That means that now,

2185
02:34:32,287 --> 02:34:33,874
You can feel pain!

2186
02:34:35,455 --> 02:34:36,518
Pain?

2187
02:34:39,831 --> 02:34:41,031
That’s why...

2188
02:34:43,109 --> 02:34:44,944
I stopped fighting you.

2189
02:34:48,199 --> 02:34:50,140
That’s why you stopped your sword.

2190
02:34:54,041 --> 02:34:55,913
You are a great knight.

2191
02:34:58,226 --> 02:34:59,526
You are human!

2192
02:35:02,752 --> 02:35:04,069
Pain...

2193
02:35:04,938 --> 02:35:06,714
Is proof of life!

2194
02:35:09,102 --> 02:35:11,751
So this is what it means to be human?

2195
02:35:12,797 --> 02:35:17,281
Because of this pain, I can also feel
the joy of being alive in this moment.

2196
02:35:27,978 --> 02:35:32,286
I feel a bizarre sense of peace now.

2197
02:35:34,031 --> 02:35:35,031
Bruford...

2198
02:35:38,034 --> 02:35:41,338
I dedicate to you the word
engraved in my sword.

2199
02:35:43,290 --> 02:35:44,825
Luck!

2200
02:35:46,009 --> 02:35:47,222
And also...

2201
02:35:47,500 --> 02:35:49,714
Pluck!

2202
02:35:56,891 --> 02:36:01,682
To think, I had to kill him
in order to save his soul...

2203
02:36:02,916 --> 02:36:05,442
Damn you!

2204
02:36:08,139 --> 02:36:13,358
JoJo!

2205
02:36:20,887 --> 02:36:25,983
I can’t believe you actually
defeated the Dark Knight!

2206
02:36:28,029 --> 02:36:30,051
Just as I thought...

2207
02:36:30,149 --> 02:36:32,236
I, Dio, will—

2208
02:36:36,028 --> 02:36:37,028
Hey baby!

2209
02:36:37,566 --> 02:36:40,955
I bet the blow from that
ripple-charged flower must hurt!

2210
02:36:41,071 --> 02:36:42,535
What the...

2211
02:36:42,693 --> 02:36:49,097
Your ripple is more vulgar than frog piss!

2212
02:36:53,684 --> 02:36:55,000
Watch out, Mr. Joestar!

2213
02:37:03,147 --> 02:37:05,766
What an embarrassment of a knight!

2214
02:37:06,465 --> 02:37:09,369
He never got his revenge!

2215
02:37:09,517 --> 02:37:12,492
What did he have to be joyful about!

2216
02:37:12,587 --> 02:37:13,587
JoJo!

2217
02:37:23,739 --> 02:37:24,903
No!

2218
02:37:25,406 --> 02:37:28,850
How could you!

2219
02:37:31,927 --> 02:37:33,677
For victory!

2220
02:37:36,885 --> 02:37:40,720
I take pride in victory!

2221
02:37:41,048 --> 02:37:42,787
Fuck!

2222
02:37:42,806 --> 02:37:44,250
I’ll get you!

2223
02:37:44,268 --> 02:37:45,734
I’ll get you for this!

2224
02:37:47,367 --> 02:37:48,367
JoJo...

2225
02:37:50,340 --> 02:37:51,340
JoJo!

2226
02:37:51,597 --> 02:37:53,740
My final ripple...

2227
02:37:54,500 --> 02:37:56,355
My... dying wish is...

2228
02:37:58,684 --> 02:38:02,581
That you take my ripple
and continue on, JoJo!

2229
02:38:18,974 --> 02:38:20,663
He collapsed.

2230
02:38:31,221 --> 02:38:34,909
I’ll vanquish your wicked soul!

2231
02:38:36,293 --> 02:38:39,912
Drown in the murk of history, Tarkus!

2232
02:38:47,162 --> 02:38:48,559
Old man!

2233
02:38:50,468 --> 02:38:51,468
Mr. Zeppeli!

2234
02:38:52,153 --> 02:38:53,439
If we lose you—

2235
02:38:53,458 --> 02:38:55,410
There’s no time to be sad.

2236
02:38:55,596 --> 02:38:58,058
The Stone Mask must be destroyed!

2237
02:38:58,303 --> 02:38:59,517
Old man!

2238
02:38:59,953 --> 02:39:00,953
I...

2239
02:39:01,778 --> 02:39:04,704
I lived my own life to the fullest.

2240
02:39:05,592 --> 02:39:07,076
In the end,

2241
02:39:07,785 --> 02:39:10,781
I leave everything I have to you.

2242
02:39:12,189 --> 02:39:13,189
JoJo,

2243
02:39:13,578 --> 02:39:15,982
You are my hope.

2244
02:39:23,251 --> 02:39:32,951
<i>Once again, life is
spilling out of my arms</i>

2245
02:39:34,969 --> 02:39:41,745
<i>You showed me my purpose</i>

2246
02:39:43,385 --> 02:39:45,384
<i>Who I am meant to be</i>

2247
02:39:47,432 --> 02:39:57,253
<i>You taught me that humanity’s
greatest gift is courage</i>

2248
02:39:59,340 --> 02:40:05,879
<i>The light you’ve given
to me will shine through</i>

2249
02:40:06,450 --> 02:40:09,645
<i>Into my spirit</i>

2250
02:40:12,451 --> 02:40:13,737
It felt like...

2251
02:40:13,765 --> 02:40:17,272
I had a friend and a son
in you at the same time.

2252
02:40:17,814 --> 02:40:19,543
From here on...

2253
02:40:20,152 --> 02:40:22,175
I live within you.

2254
02:40:23,074 --> 02:40:24,226
JoJo.

2255
02:40:28,152 --> 02:40:33,293
<i>Everything is connected</i>

2256
02:40:34,086 --> 02:40:39,605
<i>There’s a meaning to it all</i>

2257
02:40:40,398 --> 02:40:45,649
<i>That’s what I’ve come to believe</i>

2258
02:40:46,299 --> 02:40:49,274
<i>Even this pain...</i>

2259
02:40:52,304 --> 02:40:55,505
<i>Even this pain</i>

2260
02:40:58,381 --> 02:41:08,472
<i>My father left to me
what you leave to me now</i>

2261
02:41:10,463 --> 02:41:20,522
<i>The golden light that
shines from within me</i>

2262
02:41:21,482 --> 02:41:32,666
<i>It’s the one thing in my heart
that I can hold on to now</i>

2263
02:41:33,847 --> 02:41:38,228
<i>I embrace it tightly</i>

2264
02:41:39,297 --> 02:41:42,871
<i>And from this prison...</i>

2265
02:41:45,447 --> 02:41:47,915
<i>I see the stars</i>

2266
02:41:48,405 --> 02:41:54,232
<i>A golden spirit</i>

2267
02:41:54,499 --> 02:42:00,249
<i>Humanity’s glow in the darkness</i>

2268
02:42:00,927 --> 02:42:06,183
<i>Will light up</i>

2269
02:42:06,568 --> 02:42:10,748
<i>The way to you...</i>

2270
02:42:11,741 --> 02:42:12,675
Dio!

2271
02:42:12,759 --> 02:42:17,932
<i>Light up the way to you...</i>

2272
02:42:47,253 --> 02:42:49,084
JoJo...!

2273
02:42:57,753 --> 02:43:01,146
<i>Dio...</i>

2274
02:43:01,862 --> 02:43:05,298
<i>Dio...</i>

2275
02:43:06,101 --> 02:43:10,026
<i>Can’t you hear my voice?</i>

2276
02:43:10,354 --> 02:43:14,334
<i>The voice calling for you?</i>

2277
02:43:14,405 --> 02:43:18,357
<i>I can’t hear you</i>

2278
02:43:14,761 --> 02:43:18,395
{\an8}<i>Dio...</i>

2279
02:43:18,881 --> 02:43:22,400
<i>I already killed my past</i>

2280
02:43:18,905 --> 02:43:22,444
{\an8}<i>Dio...</i>

2281
02:43:22,470 --> 02:43:26,701
<i>Don’t call my name—</i>

2282
02:43:26,858 --> 02:43:31,418
<i>You and I are different</i>

2283
02:43:31,672 --> 02:43:35,537
<i>We’re not so different, you’re my son</i>

2284
02:43:35,584 --> 02:43:39,623
<i>I have changed into something new</i>

2285
02:43:39,694 --> 02:43:43,894
<i>You’re not so changed,
you did it to survive</i>

2286
02:43:44,005 --> 02:43:46,011
<i>I’ll use any means</i>

2287
02:43:46,035 --> 02:43:48,170
<i>DIO: I’ll steal it all
DARIO: You’ll steal it all</i>

2288
02:43:48,208 --> 02:43:52,474
<i>DIO: Upend righteousness</i>

2289
02:43:50,352 --> 02:43:53,902
<i>DARIO: You’re my clever boy!</i>

2290
02:43:52,546 --> 02:43:56,663
<i>DIO: I will conquer it all</i>

2291
02:43:54,608 --> 02:43:59,061
<i>DARIO: What will you want next?</i>

2292
02:43:57,792 --> 02:44:01,265
<i>DIO: I will dominate everything</i>

2293
02:44:01,314 --> 02:44:06,178
<i>Go ahead and dominate,
what will you want after that?</i>

2294
02:44:06,257 --> 02:44:10,724
<i>What do I want?</i>

2295
02:44:08,860 --> 02:44:13,373
<i>DARIO: What do you want?</i>

2296
02:44:10,765 --> 02:44:13,336
<i>DIO: What do I want?</i>

2297
02:44:13,425 --> 02:44:15,066
<i>I want...</i>

2298
02:44:15,151 --> 02:44:19,181
<i>I want...</i>

2299
02:44:16,440 --> 02:44:25,196
{\an8}<i>Dio... Dio...</i>

2300
02:44:19,247 --> 02:44:26,628
<i>I want...</i>

2301
02:44:32,760 --> 02:44:34,189
So you’ve come...

2302
02:44:36,334 --> 02:44:40,619
JoJo.

2303
02:44:41,252 --> 02:44:42,531
Is this...

2304
02:44:46,097 --> 02:44:48,122
The world you wished for?

2305
02:44:51,746 --> 02:44:52,746
What?

2306
02:44:56,890 --> 02:44:57,890
The world...

2307
02:45:01,565 --> 02:45:04,323
That you’ve been trying
to obtain for so long...

2308
02:45:09,224 --> 02:45:11,123
Surrounded by death...

2309
02:45:12,737 --> 02:45:14,118
It’s a pitiful world, isn’t it?

2310
02:45:18,424 --> 02:45:21,664
It’s a splendid world where
I’ve dominated everything.

2311
02:45:22,153 --> 02:45:25,438
I’ve dominated death, and even history too.

2312
02:45:25,500 --> 02:45:28,512
For that reason, you stole
from uninvolved innocents?

2313
02:45:32,402 --> 02:45:37,100
They were a noble sacrifice for
the sake of the future that I designed.

2314
02:45:40,393 --> 02:45:41,655
You’re just afraid.

2315
02:45:44,415 --> 02:45:45,462
Of being human...

2316
02:45:49,765 --> 02:45:51,506
That’s why you rejected your humanity.

2317
02:45:56,097 --> 02:45:57,605
For the sake of obtaining this world...

2318
02:45:58,989 --> 02:46:00,638
I’ve <i>transcended</i> humanity!

2319
02:46:00,687 --> 02:46:01,907
You ran away from it.

2320
02:46:12,773 --> 02:46:14,905
The ends justify the means.

2321
02:46:17,900 --> 02:46:19,405
I will win,

2322
02:46:21,306 --> 02:46:24,548
And that means conquering
everything, of course.

2323
02:46:26,134 --> 02:46:28,796
All of this is fate!

2324
02:46:28,843 --> 02:46:29,993
No!

2325
02:46:31,445 --> 02:46:33,355
This is just how you
chose to live your life!

2326
02:46:35,076 --> 02:46:36,424
Opposing fate...

2327
02:46:38,281 --> 02:46:39,979
What will your legacy be?

2328
02:46:43,525 --> 02:46:45,460
Such righteousness!

2329
02:46:53,466 --> 02:46:57,051
Just like the one who gave me this power...

2330
02:46:58,802 --> 02:47:00,660
And then died!

2331
02:47:05,082 --> 02:47:06,701
Just like...

2332
02:47:08,790 --> 02:47:12,945
Your father.

2333
02:47:16,919 --> 02:47:19,267
That’s right.

2334
02:47:28,257 --> 02:47:30,237
As a gentleman, it pains
me to say this, but...

2335
02:47:33,474 --> 02:47:35,335
Now I, Jonathan Joestar...

2336
02:47:38,851 --> 02:47:40,339
For the sake of revenge...

2337
02:47:42,140 --> 02:47:43,140
Dio...

2338
02:47:45,612 --> 02:47:47,314
I will kill you!

2339
02:47:47,565 --> 02:47:51,481
We’re one and the same; you want
to exact your revenge! I admire that!

2340
02:47:51,542 --> 02:47:53,846
No! I’ve come to right your wrongs!

2341
02:47:53,894 --> 02:47:55,738
I’ve accepted this as my legacy!

2342
02:47:55,778 --> 02:47:56,481
Speedwagon!

2343
02:47:56,514 --> 02:47:57,227
Right!

2344
02:48:00,343 --> 02:48:06,574
<i>Ironic, isn’t it? Now
you’re the have-not, JoJo!</i>

2345
02:48:06,683 --> 02:48:09,716
<i>I’ll suck you dry</i>

2346
02:48:09,749 --> 02:48:12,229
<i>Become my next meal!</i>

2347
02:48:13,170 --> 02:48:19,222
<i>I’ve lost so many loved ones but
their light lives on in me, Dio!</i>

2348
02:48:19,522 --> 02:48:25,266
<i>I’ve come to cleanse
your corrupted ambitions</i>

2349
02:48:26,168 --> 02:48:27,919
<i>Useless, useless, useless, useless!</i>

2350
02:48:29,129 --> 02:48:32,040
<i>I obtained this power</i>

2351
02:48:32,309 --> 02:48:35,408
<i>My heart’s aflame</i>

2352
02:48:35,490 --> 02:48:38,659
<i>So I could steal everything from you</i>

2353
02:48:38,735 --> 02:48:41,735
<i>I’ll dull this pain</i>

2354
02:48:41,901 --> 02:48:44,890
<i>If you think about it, you’re just like me</i>

2355
02:48:44,968 --> 02:48:48,148
<i>You were just like me,
two sides of the same coin</i>

2356
02:48:48,234 --> 02:48:52,922
<i>Like fire and ice, my body is burning</i>

2357
02:48:52,987 --> 02:48:55,322
<i>JOJO: I’ll kill you
DIO: You’ll kill me</i>

2358
02:48:59,421 --> 02:49:01,373
<i>JOJO: You’ll kill me
DIO: I’ll kill you</i>

2359
02:49:02,013 --> 02:49:03,560
Just like Mr. Zeppeli taught me!

2360
02:49:03,735 --> 02:49:06,007
I’ll channel my ripple through this sword!

2361
02:49:06,038 --> 02:49:09,058
You did it! You defeated Dio!

2362
02:49:09,107 --> 02:49:10,433
Not a chance!

2363
02:49:10,746 --> 02:49:12,277
You fools!

2364
02:49:13,813 --> 02:49:15,368
What! The sword is freezing—

2365
02:49:17,442 --> 02:49:20,543
Utterly pathetic!

2366
02:49:20,568 --> 02:49:21,804
Mr. Joestar!

2367
02:49:22,123 --> 02:49:23,920
JoJo!

2368
02:49:26,501 --> 02:49:32,514
<i>Utterly pathetic! I’m grasping
your carotid artery, JoJo!</i>

2369
02:49:32,787 --> 02:49:38,787
<i>With this, you’ll become
one of my undead servants</i>

2370
02:49:39,241 --> 02:49:40,973
<i>Ironic, isn’t it, Dio?</i>

2371
02:49:41,034 --> 02:49:45,539
<i>Just as I thought, you were
running away from humanity</i>

2372
02:49:45,715 --> 02:49:50,931
<i>Why don’t you freeze me now, Dio!</i>

2373
02:49:51,894 --> 02:49:53,791
My fist... Just from hitting him!

2374
02:49:53,856 --> 02:49:57,116
I transcended humanity!
None of you are on my level.

2375
02:49:58,510 --> 02:50:01,666
<i>You’re nothing but a monkey, JoJo!</i>

2376
02:50:01,726 --> 02:50:04,850
<i>JOJO: No, for as long as I have faith,
DIO: Compared to me, Dio!</i>

2377
02:50:04,954 --> 02:50:07,794
<i>DIO: Let’s test your willpower
JOJO: I will reach you!</i>

2378
02:50:07,853 --> 02:50:11,053
<i>As long as we have faith, we can grow</i>

2379
02:50:11,115 --> 02:50:14,311
<i>JOJO: Us humans...
DIO: To be human is to have limits</i>

2380
02:50:14,373 --> 02:50:17,665
<i>JOJO: That’s what he taught me
DIO: You can’t reach me!</i>

2381
02:50:17,727 --> 02:50:20,686
<i>Like fire and ice</i>

2382
02:50:20,763 --> 02:50:26,863
<i>DIO: I’ll chip away at this body to prove it
JOJO: I’ll burn up this body to prove it</i>

2383
02:50:28,667 --> 02:50:30,511
He put his hand in the
fire! If he does that—

2384
02:50:30,564 --> 02:50:33,571
<i>Like fire and ice</i>

2385
02:50:33,631 --> 02:50:36,671
<i>My lost friends, my father’s spirit</i>

2386
02:50:36,918 --> 02:50:39,946
<i>Like fire and ice</i>

2387
02:50:40,007 --> 02:50:43,249
<i>JOJO: Our connection, it’s here
DIO: Even when I’ve thrown away my humanity</i>

2388
02:50:43,318 --> 02:50:46,225
<i>Like fire and ice</i>

2389
02:50:46,311 --> 02:50:50,033
<i>With my life on the
line, I’ll prove it now!</i>

2390
02:50:50,103 --> 02:50:54,284
<i>-Dio! Dio! Dio!
-JoJo! JoJo! JoJo!</i>

2391
02:50:57,542 --> 02:50:59,636
“I was only trying to be friendly!”

2392
02:51:00,063 --> 02:51:02,046
“I like being number one!”

2393
02:51:05,036 --> 02:51:06,075
“My eye!”

2394
02:51:06,127 --> 02:51:08,376
“I think my finger went in his eye.”

2395
02:51:12,624 --> 02:51:13,624
Dio!

2396
02:51:15,246 --> 02:51:22,670
<i>I won’t stop beating you
until you’re finished!</i>

2397
02:51:29,846 --> 02:51:31,001
This is impossible!

2398
02:51:31,571 --> 02:51:33,804
The heat is coursing through me!

2399
02:51:34,303 --> 02:51:35,554
I’m melting!

2400
02:51:35,593 --> 02:51:36,878
Crumble to dust!

2401
02:51:36,923 --> 02:51:39,137
I can’t be...

2402
02:51:40,173 --> 02:51:42,236
Not yet!!

2403
02:51:45,324 --> 02:51:49,537
Watch out! He’s shooting
hot liquid out of his eyes!

2404
02:51:49,608 --> 02:51:53,183
Lord Dio...!

2405
02:52:02,355 --> 02:52:03,355
Dio...!

2406
02:52:19,130 --> 02:52:21,860
<i>Extra, extra! Read all about it!</i>

2407
02:52:22,671 --> 02:52:27,116
<i>(In 1888 on December the 4th)</i>

2408
02:52:27,283 --> 02:52:29,767
<i>(The London Press reported)</i>

2409
02:52:29,792 --> 02:52:31,593
<i>There was a small incident</i>

2410
02:52:31,640 --> 02:52:33,522
<i>(In Windknight’s Lot)</i>

2411
02:52:33,560 --> 02:52:38,282
<i>(That little village, there was
a missing persons incident)</i>

2412
02:52:38,321 --> 02:52:40,321
<i>A very bizarre case</i>

2413
02:52:40,345 --> 02:52:42,527
<i>73 people vanished</i>

2414
02:52:42,647 --> 02:52:44,617
<i>In just one night,
they abruptly disappeared</i>

2415
02:52:44,642 --> 02:52:47,024
<i>Moaning could be heard from underground</i>

2416
02:52:47,075 --> 02:52:49,249
<i>But no one was found</i>

2417
02:52:49,308 --> 02:52:53,224
<i>(In 1888 on December the 15th)</i>

2418
02:52:53,285 --> 02:52:55,750
<i>(In the Windknight’s Lot Paper)</i>

2419
02:52:55,776 --> 02:52:57,705
<i>An eye-witness reported</i>

2420
02:52:57,729 --> 02:52:59,822
<i>That the following day, below a cliff</i>

2421
02:52:59,845 --> 02:53:01,718
<i>Men were seen burning clothing</i>

2422
02:53:01,745 --> 02:53:04,563
<i>(And destroying something with a hammer)</i>

2423
02:53:04,590 --> 02:53:06,207
<i>It seemed to be a stone mask</i>

2424
02:53:06,265 --> 02:53:10,382
<i>(In 1889 on February the 2nd)</i>

2425
02:53:10,427 --> 02:53:14,048
<i>(In the announcements section)</i>

2426
02:53:14,191 --> 02:53:18,697
<i>(The Joestar heir)</i>

2427
02:53:18,771 --> 02:53:22,785
<i>(Jonathan Joestar, of Liverpool, was wed)</i>

2428
02:53:22,865 --> 02:53:28,403
<i>(To the Pendletons’
daughter, Erina Pendleton)</i>

2429
02:53:28,837 --> 02:53:30,513
<i>In a small notice, they announced:</i>

2430
02:53:30,550 --> 02:53:35,092
<i>The honeymoon would be a trip
to the United States by steamer</i>

2431
02:53:35,139 --> 02:53:38,568
<i>(Now, on to other news...)</i>

2432
02:53:40,447 --> 02:53:42,352
Mr. Joestar! Both of you!

2433
02:53:42,372 --> 02:53:43,911
Best of wishes!

2434
02:53:44,161 --> 02:53:46,120
I’ll always be there for you!

2435
02:53:46,185 --> 02:53:49,789
If you’re in trouble, I’ll rush anywhere!

2436
02:53:49,870 --> 02:53:52,027
Happy honeymoon!

2437
02:53:52,056 --> 02:53:54,904
I can’t wait to hear all about it!

2438
02:53:55,549 --> 02:53:57,549
America, how nice!

2439
02:53:57,902 --> 02:54:00,116
I wanna go there too,

2440
02:54:00,145 --> 02:54:02,742
And try to dig up some oil for myself!

2441
02:54:03,203 --> 02:54:04,727
Damn it...

2442
02:54:05,918 --> 02:54:09,601
But after this, a fateful
moment was soon to come...

2443
02:54:10,112 --> 02:54:14,302
This story will be passed down
until the world has come full circle.

2444
02:54:14,355 --> 02:54:19,149
That will be the life’s work
of Speedwagon the meddler...

2445
02:54:19,516 --> 02:54:24,044
But, the one to tell you what
happens right now won’t be me...

2446
02:54:32,531 --> 02:54:37,341
<i>I pray that today will never end</i>

2447
02:54:37,387 --> 02:54:40,490
<i>In the midst of a carousel of stars</i>

2448
02:54:41,063 --> 02:54:49,438
<i>Let my hand always be in yours</i>

2449
02:54:49,795 --> 02:54:51,097
What’s wrong?

2450
02:54:54,408 --> 02:54:56,361
When you’re next to me...

2451
02:54:57,169 --> 02:54:58,586
I’m happy!

2452
02:54:58,997 --> 02:55:00,632
I feel the same.

2453
02:55:01,023 --> 02:55:03,118
I wish you could’ve met my father...

2454
02:55:03,935 --> 02:55:05,744
Well, let’s go and eat!

2455
02:55:10,721 --> 02:55:11,721
Jonathan?

2456
02:55:12,568 --> 02:55:13,568
That’s...

2457
02:55:17,567 --> 02:55:18,567
Erina,

2458
02:55:19,625 --> 02:55:21,062
Go back to our cabin.

2459
02:55:21,788 --> 02:55:23,735
Don’t forget to lock the door!

2460
02:55:34,352 --> 02:55:36,459
I have lured him here.

2461
02:55:37,127 --> 02:55:38,823
My body...

2462
02:55:40,234 --> 02:55:41,728
Have you come?

2463
02:55:43,064 --> 02:55:44,064
Dio...

2464
02:55:44,584 --> 02:55:45,584
JoJo...

2465
02:55:47,491 --> 02:55:51,838
I dare show myself in this pitiful
state in front of you for a reason...

2466
02:55:53,517 --> 02:55:55,901
I used to despise you so much,

2467
02:55:56,171 --> 02:55:58,568
But now I respect you...

2468
02:55:59,181 --> 02:56:01,170
That’s because I’ve realised something!

2469
02:56:03,676 --> 02:56:06,932
If there is a God that controls fate,

2470
02:56:07,836 --> 02:56:11,620
Then there’s never been a relationship
orchestrated as perfectly as ours...

2471
02:56:13,138 --> 02:56:16,719
You’re the reason I got this power,

2472
02:56:17,578 --> 02:56:19,966
And you’re the reason why...

2473
02:56:20,849 --> 02:56:23,978
The world has slipped from my grasp!

2474
02:56:24,947 --> 02:56:26,284
When will it...

2475
02:56:27,377 --> 02:56:28,335
Be enough for you?

2476
02:56:28,356 --> 02:56:30,968
That’s exactly what our destiny is!

2477
02:56:32,419 --> 02:56:37,938
I’ll obtain the body of the one and
only person I respect in this world.

2478
02:56:38,640 --> 02:56:41,968
And live in eternal glory!

2479
02:56:43,364 --> 02:56:45,102
JoJo...

2480
02:56:46,248 --> 02:56:48,256
You and I...

2481
02:56:49,047 --> 02:56:52,063
Are one and the same in this world!

2482
02:56:55,531 --> 02:56:58,214
Lord Dio! Look, look, look!

2483
02:56:58,243 --> 02:57:00,401
Please look!

2484
02:57:01,040 --> 02:57:02,453
Jonathan!

2485
02:57:04,450 --> 02:57:06,781
<i>From light to darkness</i>

2486
02:57:06,815 --> 02:57:08,918
<i>This is the start of my mythos</i>

2487
02:57:08,944 --> 02:57:11,105
<i>I will end it all</i>

2488
02:57:11,130 --> 02:57:13,154
<i>And restart it all</i>

2489
02:57:13,434 --> 02:57:15,855
<i>For this is Dio’s World!</i>

2490
02:57:15,879 --> 02:57:17,434
Right, Erina Joestar?

2491
02:57:17,449 --> 02:57:18,282
Dio!

2492
02:57:18,330 --> 02:57:22,084
<i>I can’t speak—can’t breathe—</i>

2493
02:57:22,613 --> 02:57:24,170
<i>My ripple!</i>

2494
02:57:24,430 --> 02:57:26,454
Erina! Not you too!

2495
02:57:27,145 --> 02:57:30,502
<i>This is the start of his mythos!</i>

2496
02:57:30,562 --> 02:57:36,196
<i>This ark is swarming with his followers!</i>

2497
02:57:38,100 --> 02:57:39,298
Please, spare the child!

2498
02:57:40,058 --> 02:57:41,058
Run!

2499
02:57:41,282 --> 02:57:42,822
Shall we torture him to death?!

2500
02:57:42,849 --> 02:57:45,770
Or maybe enjoy watching him asphyxiate?!

2501
02:57:45,799 --> 02:57:46,887
Wang Chan!

2502
02:57:48,063 --> 02:57:52,245
<i>Painlessly cut his head
from his shoulders!</i>

2503
02:57:52,283 --> 02:57:54,577
<i>I won’t tolerate any insults!</i>

2504
02:57:54,605 --> 02:57:56,864
<i>My friend, Jonathan Joestar—</i>

2505
02:57:57,320 --> 02:58:00,532
<i>I’ll take you as my own</i>

2506
02:58:00,583 --> 02:58:06,079
<i>Your blood will become my future!</i>

2507
02:58:06,194 --> 02:58:09,592
<i>I’ll tie our futures together</i>

2508
02:58:10,299 --> 02:58:14,529
<i>With my final ripple!</i>

2509
02:58:14,632 --> 02:58:18,466
<i>JoJo!</i>

2510
02:58:18,774 --> 02:58:23,547
<i>JoJo!</i>

2511
02:58:34,031 --> 02:58:40,030
<i>I felt it tear. Something
important inside me just tore</i>

2512
02:58:40,156 --> 02:58:41,156
Jonathan!

2513
02:58:43,320 --> 02:58:45,310
ERINA: How could this be?!
JOJO: Get out of here!

2514
02:58:46,046 --> 02:58:48,045
I won’t, JoJo...

2515
02:58:48,820 --> 02:58:57,122
<i>I will burn with you</i>

2516
02:58:57,217 --> 02:59:05,392
<i>Until everything turns to ash</i>

2517
02:59:09,965 --> 02:59:12,227
<i>(The flash of flames)</i>

2518
02:59:12,300 --> 02:59:14,230
<i>Everything is connected</i>

2519
02:59:14,259 --> 02:59:16,330
<i>You can’t ask me to live!</i>

2520
02:59:16,355 --> 02:59:18,411
<i>There’s a meaning to it all!</i>

2521
02:59:18,445 --> 02:59:21,014
<i>JOJO: It’s alright if you cry
ERINA: Your courage is too cruel!</i>

2522
02:59:21,039 --> 02:59:22,870
<i>JOJO: You will be
ERINA: I will be</i>

2523
02:59:22,903 --> 02:59:26,572
<i>The one to spin the thread of fate</i>

2524
02:59:26,652 --> 02:59:30,588
{\an8}<i>(Flames are burning everything up)</i>

2525
02:59:26,991 --> 02:59:33,686
<i>Just like my mother
died for me, I’ll—</i>

2526
02:59:30,723 --> 02:59:34,937
{\an8}<i>(Light and darkness flicker and flash)</i>

2527
02:59:35,007 --> 02:59:38,666
{\an8}<i>(Flames are burning everything up)</i>

2528
02:59:35,342 --> 02:59:37,228
<i>Farewell!</i>

2529
02:59:37,249 --> 02:59:38,976
<i>I’m still alive! </i>

2530
02:59:39,255 --> 02:59:44,932
<i>In the end, I, Dio, will triumph!</i>

2531
02:59:39,269 --> 02:59:42,967
{\an8}<i>(Light and darkness flicker and flash)</i>

2532
02:59:45,228 --> 02:59:50,046
<i>My mythos begins here</i>

2533
02:59:50,091 --> 02:59:53,043
<i>JoJo!</i>

2534
02:59:59,670 --> 03:00:01,629
I know what you’re like...

2535
03:00:03,471 --> 03:00:04,802
I figured...

2536
03:00:05,782 --> 03:00:07,258
You would strike...

2537
03:00:08,511 --> 03:00:09,953
Before I...

2538
03:00:13,222 --> 03:00:14,622
Lost consciousness.

2539
03:00:17,193 --> 03:00:18,193
JoJo?

2540
03:00:19,138 --> 03:00:20,646
Let me go, JoJo!

2541
03:00:24,555 --> 03:00:25,555
He’s...

2542
03:00:29,976 --> 03:00:30,976
Dead...

2543
03:00:53,368 --> 03:00:58,049
<i>[AZTEC CHANTING]</i>

2544
03:01:07,921 --> 03:01:13,368
<i>That proud life of his</i>

2545
03:01:14,015 --> 03:01:18,068
<i>Vanished into the dusts of time</i>

2546
03:01:18,738 --> 03:01:22,958
<i>But this fateful adventure</i>

2547
03:01:23,660 --> 03:01:28,225
<i>Will become an inheritance</i>

2548
03:01:28,315 --> 03:01:31,124
<i>Passed down forever</i>

2549
03:01:33,517 --> 03:01:35,771
<i>His golden spirit</i>

2550
03:01:35,831 --> 03:01:40,007
<i>(Phantom Blood)</i>

2551
03:01:45,837 --> 03:01:48,522
<i>Like two who make one,</i>

2552
03:01:49,086 --> 03:01:52,943
<i>We feel a bizarre friendship</i>

2553
03:01:54,155 --> 03:01:57,094
<i>Isn’t that right, Dio?</i>

2554
03:01:58,040 --> 03:02:01,032
<i>If it weren’t for you...</i>

2555
03:02:01,064 --> 03:02:03,643
<i>No, it’s because of you</i>

2556
03:02:03,672 --> 03:02:05,941
<i>Hey, JoJo</i>

2557
03:02:06,550 --> 03:02:09,247
<i>Now I’ll...</i>

2558
03:02:10,153 --> 03:02:14,435
<i>Keep looking at the stars</i>

2559
03:02:14,630 --> 03:02:21,172
<i>Guided by this hapless fate</i>

2560
03:02:21,995 --> 03:02:26,283
<i>We’ll reach out to the stars</i>

2561
03:02:26,479 --> 03:02:32,753
<i>Our two fates</i>

2562
03:02:33,119 --> 03:02:36,609
<i>Have become one</i>

2563
03:02:34,257 --> 03:02:39,170
{\an8}<i>(That immortal poem echoes quietly)</i>

2564
03:02:39,247 --> 03:02:42,144
<i>Until the world</i>

2565
03:02:39,919 --> 03:02:43,870
{\an8}<i>(One saw stars)</i>

2566
03:02:44,517 --> 03:02:48,215
<i>Is born anew</i>

2567
03:02:45,420 --> 03:02:48,349
{\an8}<i>(The stars are shimmering)</i>

2568
03:02:48,458 --> 03:02:50,805
{\an8}<i>(Like blood through a vein,
mud is pulsating)</i>

2569
03:02:50,309 --> 03:02:53,629
<i>I’ll live</i>

2570
03:02:51,133 --> 03:02:55,479
{\an8}<i>(One saw mud)</i>

2571
03:02:54,295 --> 03:02:57,008
<i>I’ll disappear</i>

2572
03:02:57,178 --> 03:03:07,872
<i>JOJO: With you!
DIO: I will live!</i>

2573
03:02:58,432 --> 03:03:03,837
{\an8}<i>(The sunlight yellow gleam shines)</i>

2574
03:03:03,892 --> 03:03:08,049
{\an8}<i>(Let the golden wind blow)</i>

2575
03:03:08,104 --> 03:03:13,623
{\an8}<i>(And the shadow of midnight
blue darkness grows)</i>

2576
03:03:10,871 --> 03:03:14,319
<i>(Living in the shadow of history)</i>

2577
03:03:14,513 --> 03:03:17,494
<i>(We’ll stop the flow of time)</i>

2578
03:03:17,837 --> 03:03:20,708
<i>(Even when the world resets)</i>

2579
03:03:20,743 --> 03:03:23,767
<i>(The tale will keep on being told)</i>

2580
03:03:23,963 --> 03:03:29,995
<i>(This bizarre adventure)</i>

2581
03:03:30,939 --> 03:03:39,973
<i>(Our golden spirit will shine)</i>

2582
03:03:45,556 --> 03:03:49,152
Speedwagon coolly withdraws.

2583
03:08:27,648 --> 03:08:31,606
Thank you for coming
to today’s performance.

2584
03:08:35,828 --> 03:08:37,539
This is a public [streamed] performance.

2585
03:08:37,805 --> 03:08:42,620
Since it’s my and Zeppeli’s actor,
Hirose Yusuke’s, final performance,

2586
03:08:42,694 --> 03:08:46,239
We each wanted to say a
few words if you don’t mind.

2587
03:08:49,036 --> 03:08:50,585
Take it away, Mr. Hirose.

2588
03:08:50,644 --> 03:08:54,931
I had the honour of performing the double
cast role of Zeppeli. I am Hirose Yusuke.

2589
03:08:55,008 --> 03:08:57,008
Thank you for today.

2590
03:09:00,200 --> 03:09:02,449
The musical will close tomorrow, though.

2591
03:09:02,759 --> 03:09:06,085
This type of role has been
played by others before,

2592
03:09:06,672 --> 03:09:10,452
Although personally, I
found that to be relieving.

2593
03:09:10,768 --> 03:09:15,355
There have been many
things that led to this day.

2594
03:09:15,417 --> 03:09:21,486
So even now, I have a lot of
thoughts and a lot of emotions, but...

2595
03:09:21,795 --> 03:09:26,990
Aside from that, the fact that we
have come this far is really thanks to...

2596
03:09:27,480 --> 03:09:32,917
Each and every one of the cast members
on this stage, and the wonderful and skilled staff.

2597
03:09:33,124 --> 03:09:35,708
And foremost, the people
who came every day—

2598
03:09:35,769 --> 03:09:39,406
You’re not coming every day?
Well, every day—

2599
03:09:39,473 --> 03:09:43,027
Truly a lot of fans came
and filled the whole theatre.

2600
03:09:43,087 --> 03:09:45,443
I would like to think our performance’s
quality is thanks to your support.

2601
03:09:45,509 --> 03:09:50,222
Truly, you’ve made each member of
this performance happy. Thank you.

2602
03:09:50,289 --> 03:09:52,785
From the bottom of my heart,

2603
03:09:52,834 --> 03:09:54,431
Pow.

2604
03:09:54,476 --> 03:09:56,476
MAMORU: From the bottom of the heart, pow!

2605
03:10:08,699 --> 03:10:12,736
Well, I played the role of Jonathan
Joestar, I’m Matsushita Yuya.

2606
03:10:12,795 --> 03:10:14,795
Thank you for today!

2607
03:10:16,189 --> 03:10:18,618
Did you have fun, everyone?!

2608
03:10:19,808 --> 03:10:22,609
The best, hearing this is the best, yeah.

2609
03:10:23,073 --> 03:10:27,068
Uh, right. Really, tomorrow’s
truly the final performance.

2610
03:10:27,129 --> 03:10:29,147
That curtain call will
be the grand finale, too.

2611
03:10:29,177 --> 03:10:32,227
I think that Shotaro will
do perfectly tomorrow.

2612
03:10:32,260 --> 03:10:34,678
I—are you worried?

2613
03:10:34,719 --> 03:10:35,547
Nah, it’s probably okay.

2614
03:10:35,405 --> 03:10:37,171
-I’m worried, so please do the speech instead!

2615
03:10:36,152 --> 03:10:38,134
-He’s—that’s in the past.

2616
03:10:38,190 --> 03:10:41,635
Yeah, no. Anyway I think he’ll be fine.

2617
03:10:41,704 --> 03:10:45,854
I wanted to voice some
personal thoughts here.

2618
03:10:45,926 --> 03:10:49,794
First off, as Mr. Hirose said before,

2619
03:10:49,860 --> 03:10:53,055
It’s been a long road to
arrive at our final performance.

2620
03:10:53,109 --> 03:10:54,802
And I’m relieved that we made it.

2621
03:10:54,857 --> 03:10:58,431
Truly, I’m truly happy to
be on this stage. Thank you!

2622
03:11:03,198 --> 03:11:07,771
Back in February, right?
Opening night was delayed.

2623
03:11:07,835 --> 03:11:09,909
But when we made it to opening day,

2624
03:11:09,983 --> 03:11:16,422
At that curtain call, really, at that time,
the audience cheered and applauded a lot,

2625
03:11:16,494 --> 03:11:17,995
Which has continued up through today.

2626
03:11:18,057 --> 03:11:22,989
Truthfully, at that time, I was feeling, within
me, that we became something unforgettable.

2627
03:11:23,085 --> 03:11:30,247
Yes, that’s right. Truly,
thank you for everything.

2628
03:11:30,332 --> 03:11:33,534
For having supported us up to this point.

2629
03:11:33,590 --> 03:11:35,732
And to Mamo, who supported
me like a partner in this.

2630
03:11:35,796 --> 03:11:40,327
Isn’t it seriously amazing that
he did this role without a double?

2631
03:11:40,388 --> 03:11:41,922
MAMORU: It’s alright.
YUYA: No, it was wonderful.

2632
03:11:42,162 --> 03:11:45,159
Before you even started,
I almost cried when I saw your face.

2633
03:11:45,213 --> 03:11:47,114
Yeah, me too a bit! I got emotional!

2634
03:11:47,159 --> 03:11:48,619
MAMORU: Yes.
YUYA: Sorry, I had to excuse myself.

2635
03:11:48,658 --> 03:11:49,628
Excuse yourself...

2636
03:11:49,675 --> 03:11:52,412
YUYA: It wasn’t because of you or something like that that I left.
MAMORU: I get it.

2637
03:11:52,478 --> 03:11:56,782
Nah, you were really incredible.
Really spectacularly incredible.

2638
03:11:56,839 --> 03:11:57,914
MAMORU: Not at all.
YUYA: No, no, I’m sorry.

2639
03:11:57,969 --> 03:12:02,059
It might be unusual for a performer to say this,
but I truly respect you. Really, you’re wonderful.

2640
03:12:02,103 --> 03:12:05,446
MAMORU: No, no really.
YUYA: I thought he really rejected his humanity.

2641
03:12:05,529 --> 03:12:06,924
You were just that wonderful.

2642
03:12:06,964 --> 03:12:08,280
[INAUDIBLE]

2643
03:12:08,324 --> 03:12:10,453
MAMORU: Thanks.
YUYA: Yes. So then...

2644
03:12:10,522 --> 03:12:15,855
We’re not on the same stage
tonight as we were then, but—

2645
03:12:15,963 --> 03:12:24,939
From the first day of rehearsals until now, he’s
supported me, helped me improve, and encouraged me.

2646
03:12:25,055 --> 03:12:31,664
Shotaro too. I truly believe that without those
two, I would never have achieved this JoJo.

2647
03:12:31,867 --> 03:12:36,062
So, this has been my first time
acting in a double cast performance.

2648
03:12:36,135 --> 03:12:40,192
Thank you everyone in the cast!

2649
03:12:40,424 --> 03:12:44,302
It was wonderful. Thanks!

2650
03:12:49,223 --> 03:12:53,904
And above all, above all, truly,
thank you for being devoted like this!

2651
03:12:53,972 --> 03:12:55,468
Now to everyone at the theatre,

2652
03:12:55,529 --> 03:13:00,110
And everyone watching the stream,
I don’t know where the cameras are but—

2653
03:13:00,176 --> 03:13:02,700
Thank you from the bottom of my heart!

2654
03:13:05,243 --> 03:13:05,949
Thanks!

2655
03:13:10,411 --> 03:13:13,594
I was already so relieved that
I could raise my voice today.

2656
03:13:13,717 --> 03:13:19,532
Yes, and tomorrow Mr. Hirose and I will
be watching the final performance together!

2657
03:13:19,604 --> 03:13:21,810
Everyone, do your best!

2658
03:13:21,860 --> 03:13:23,860
I’ll be giving it my all along with you!

2659
03:13:25,620 --> 03:13:28,793
Everyone, make sure
to—what are you saying?

2660
03:13:28,856 --> 03:13:32,213
I’m doing it! I was
just getting to it, okay?!

2661
03:13:32,362 --> 03:13:34,769
I’m gonna watch it too!

2662
03:13:36,384 --> 03:13:38,716
Yeah, I’ll watch too.

2663
03:13:39,172 --> 03:13:40,063
Pardon me.

2664
03:13:40,133 --> 03:13:46,942
And so, please support everyone
through tomorrow’s final performance!

2665
03:13:55,368 --> 03:13:59,299
Truly, thank you for today!

2666
03:13:59,369 --> 03:14:03,369
{\an8}[TN: Everyone’s muted for about 2 min]

2667
03:16:23,911 --> 03:16:25,982
[INAUDIBLE]

2668
03:16:26,059 --> 03:16:27,352
MAMORU: It’s already over.

2669
03:16:27,392 --> 03:16:28,648
[INAUDIBLE]

2670
03:16:28,721 --> 03:16:31,601
Thank you! Thank you!

2671
03:16:31,658 --> 03:16:34,167
Definitely, please support
tomorrow’s performance too!

2672
03:16:34,219 --> 03:16:36,404
Shotaro, do your best tomorrow!

2673
03:16:36,451 --> 03:16:38,173
MAMORU: Do your best!

2674
03:16:39,364 --> 03:16:40,870
Thank you!

2675
03:16:41,786 --> 03:16:42,872
MAMORU: Thanks!

